title: FA Cup Highlights 2014-04-12 720p HDTV-wAm.mkv
description:
SPORT: FA Cup Highlights
On: itv Central HD
Date: Saturday 12th April 2014

The best of the action from the FA Cup semi-final between Arsenal and Wigan Athletic as Arsenal continue to look to end their nine-year trophy drought, and Wigan hope to get back to the Final for a chance to retain the Cup they won so dramatically last season. Commentary is from Clive Tyldesley and Andy Townse
